title: Climate change joke makes a bad day worse
text:
Social Services Minister Scott Morrison, Prime Minister Tony Abbott and Immigration Minister Peter Dutton. Will all three have the same jobs int he weeks after the canning by-election Alex Ellinghausen Mr Dutton said: "Time doesn't mean anything when you're about to have water lapping at your door". He and Mr Abbott chuckled until Social Services Minister Scott Morrison warned both colleagues there was a boom microphone hovering above them.
Mr Dutton said later he would not comment on a "private conversation".
